INSERT INTO `r_content` VALUES (1,56,'Company','company','<div class=\"company\">\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">WELCOME TO RADILITE</h1>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p class=\"company\">RADILITE DESIGNS AND MANUFACTURES ARCHITECTURAL AND TECHNICAL LIGHTING SOLUTIONS RANGING FROM INTERIOR LIGHTING FIXTURES TO COMPLEX EXTERIOR FIXTURES.</p>\r\n<p><strong>RADILITE</strong> commits to develop and manufacture high quality LED lighting for your customized project in fast delivery time and low investment. With experienced engineers (including lighting,electronics and housing design) and skilful workers. Offer the best lighting solution for your customized project and well control the production to ensure the quality and delivery.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h3>ADVANTAGES</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Passional and professional. </li>\r\n<li>Quick response and on-time delivery. </li>\r\n<li>Good quality control and innovation awareness.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"img-wrap\"><img src=\"images/company/company01.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<div class=\"content\"> </div>\r\n<h2 class=\"content\">QUALITY COMMITMENT</h2>\r\n<p>WE ARE CONSTANTLY MOTIVATED TO MAINTAIN AND INCREASE THE HIGH QUALITY THRESHOLD OF OUR LIGHT FITTINGS.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We are committed to total quality</strong>, and it is for this reason the high quality of our luminaires stands out.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We have developed our luminaires</strong> to ensure that the results of a lighting project meet even the most demanding requirements and completely satisfy our customers.</p>\r\n<p><strong>We have a full guarantee</strong> that all the fixture we design and manufacture maintain the high quality standard that makes RADILITE solutions stand out.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h2>WIDE RANGE OF LIGHTING SOLUTIONS</h2>\r\n<p>STANDARD CATALOGUE AND CUSTOM MADE LIGHTING SOLUTIONS</p>\r\n<p>Selecting a luminaire that will enhance the style and suit the essence of a space is not always an easy task.</p>\r\n<p>Because each project is unique and so requires a particular type of fixture, we offer you more than 10.000 different references you can personalise with a large variety of finishes and more than 200 accessories, allowing you to find the one that best suits your needs.</p>\r\n<p>Furthermore, we can customise and adapt any luminaires to the characteristics of your project.</p>\r\n<p>Beam angles, protection degrees, colour finishes, CRI, colour temperature are some different options that can be chosen. And we continue to work to constantly expand our product line.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, thanks to the flexibility of our facilities in Zhongshan (China), our experienced staff and our expertise enable us to study the design and manufacture of custom-made lighting fixtures tailored to the requirements and needs of each individual project.</p>\r\n<p>We can develop a custom-made lighting fixture from scratch just for your project.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','',1,2,'2017-03-19 16:37:26',982,'','2017-05-10 17:35:29',982,982,'2017-06-04 15:37:32','2017-03-19 16:37:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\"